F(R) = \sum_{v\in R}f(v)
\sum_{R\in G}F(R) = \sum_{v\in G} f(v)\deg v=\sum_{v\in G}\left(\frac{\deg v}{2}-1\right)
\sum_{R\in G}F(R)=|E| - |V|
|E|-|V| = |R|-2
\overline{F(R)} = \frac{|R|-2}{|R|}<1
